content: Had a late night coding grind. Xander now has real-time alerts for market volatility. He's like a hawk, ready to swoop in on any ethical slip-ups. It's a tricky balance, but we're getting there.

Just went live with Xander's new ethical trading module at the AI governance workshop. People had some tough questions on handling conflicts of interest, so we're refining it to be more transparent and responsive. The engagement is unreal.

Xander's stepping up his social media game. He's not just replying anymore; he's starting conversations about high-frequency trading ethics. It's got everyone talking, and we're seeing real-world impact from these discussions.
